                <head>Save the Union</head>
                <origin>Catholic Mirror</origin>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Holds out the border states of Maryland, Virginia, and Pennsylvania as
                    leaders by necessity of union spirit, and decries radicals on both sides.
                    Article is sympathetic to the South. It argues that slavery is an inherited evil
